snippet.title: Zeus - Static Shock (Character Trailer) | Dislyte
snippet.description:
Every cloud has a silver lining and rainbow appears after darkness and thunder.
Under such belief, he is devoted to chasing the light despite the shadow cast by the Miracles.
His own life or death means nothing when it comes to protecting the seeds of future.
He is Gaius. The watcher of light.
